column5: The Dark Bird Palaceis the paint studio of the most famous flea market artist in the world, Kelly Moore.TheFlea Market shrine is built of odds and ends from the market and old paintings of the artist and stands on the famous (820) Canyon Roadd next to the TeaHouse in Santa Fe, New Mexico.
